label: Urban or rural site
codebookDescription: Location of the household when the child was born, urban or rural

label: Age at anthropometry
codebookDescription: Age when the last anthropometry measurements were taken.

label: Height-for-age z-score
codebookDescription: Height-for-age z-score at the last measurement point

label: Weight-for-age z-score
codebookDescription: Weight-for-age z-score at the last measurement point

label: BMI-for-age z-score
codebookDescription: BMI-for-age z-score at the last measurement point

label: Linear growth during 1st year
codebookDescription: Linear growth during the first year of life.

label: Weight gain during 1st year
codebookDescription: Weight gain during the first year of life.

label: Mean linear growth during 1st 3 years
codebookDescription: Average linear growth pace during first three years of life.

label: Mean weight gain during 1st 3 years
codebookDescription: Average weight gain during first three years of life.

label: Breastfeeding duration
codebookDescription: Total time breastfed, until weaning

label: Exclusive breastfeeding duration
codebookDescription: Total time exclusively breastfed, until introduced to solid food(s)

label: Age
codebookDescription: Age at stool sample collection.

label: Age at two autoantibodies positive
codebookDescription: Age when two different autoantibodies were measured positive, i.e. Seroconversion

label: Insulin autoantibodies
codebookDescription: Child has measured positive for insulin autoantibodies (IAA)

label: Insulinoma-associated protein 2 autoantibodies
codebookDescription: Child has measured positive for insulinoma-associated protein 2 autoantibody (IA2A)

label: Glutamic acid decarboxylase autoantibodies
codebookDescription: Child has measured positive for Glutamic acid decarboxylase antibodies (GADA)
repeated: Child has measured positive for Islet cell autoantibodies (ICA)

label: Zinc transporter 8 autoantibodies
codebookDescription: Child has measured positive for Zinc transporter 8 autoantibody (ZnT8A)

label: Age at type 1 diabetes diagnosis
codebookDescription: Age when the child was diagnosed type 1 diabetes

label: HLA risk, by HLA haplotyping
codebookDescription: HLA (human leukocyte antigen) risk class for T1D and autoimmunity determined by HLA haplotyping, value between 1-4, 1=slightly increase risk, 4=high risk.

label: Diet in first three days
codebookDescription: Milk feeding during the first three days of life: mother's breast milk, formula or something else (e.g. combination of beast milk and formula, or not reported)

label: Age 1st animal milk or solids given
codebookDescription: Approximate age when the child first received solid food or non-human milk.

label: Mom reported antibiotic use during pregnancy
codebookDescription: Whether the mother reported having gestational diabetes during pregnancy.

label: Sample type
codebookDescription: Whetther the mother reported taking antibiotics during pregnancy.
